log.content: I would like you to create an svg image of a sunset through the mountains. Make sure the result is visible in index.html

This will create an `index.html` file with a basic SVG element. You can then fill in the content of the SVG to create your sunset through the mountains image.

Note: This is just a starting point, and you will need to add more code to create the actual SVG image. The `create_file` function only creates a new file with the specified content, it doesn't generate any images.
